<view class="app-page tp"><view class="tp-head app-card app-card--glass"><text class="tp-title">体温（℃）</text><text class="tp-sub">用于观察发热/感染等风险信号。数据写入后将自动展示趋势。</text></view><view class="tp-main app-card"><view class="tp-main-row flex-row items-center justify-between"><view class="flex-col"><text class="tp-main-label">当前体温</text><text class="tp-main-hint">最近一次测量值</text></view><view class="tp-main-right"><text class="tp-val">{{a}}</text><text class="tp-unit">℃</text><view class="{{['tp-chip', c]}}">{{b}}</view></view></view></view><view class="tp-trend app-card app-card--glass"><view class="tp-trend-head flex-row items-center justify-between"><text class="tp-trend-title">近7天趋势</text><view class="btn-secondary tp-trend-btn" bindtap="{{d}}">查看详情</view></view><view wx:if="{{e}}" class="tp-empty"><text class="tp-empty-title">暂无数据</text><text class="tp-empty-sub">请先在「设备管理」手动补录体温，或后续对接体温设备同步。</text><view class="tp-empty-actions flex-row"><view class="btn-secondary tp-empty-btn" bindtap="{{f}}">去补录</view><view class="btn-secondary tp-empty-btn ml-12" bindtap="{{g}}">查看趋势</view></view></view><view wx:else class="tp-bars"><view wx:for="{{h}}" wx:for-item="p" wx:key="c" class="tp-bar"><view class="tp-bar-inner" style="{{'height:' + p.a}}"></view><text class="tp-bar-x">{{p.b}}</text></view></view><view wx:if="{{i}}" class="tp-stats"><text class="tp-stat">平均：{{j}}℃</text><text class="tp-stat">最高：{{k}}℃</text><text class="tp-stat">最低：{{l}}℃</text></view></view><view class="tp-tips app-card"><text class="tp-tips-title">测量要点</text><view class="tp-tip">1. 建议每日同一时间测量（如早起、晚睡前），避免运动后立即测量。</view><view class="tp-tip">2. 若体温 ≥ 37.3℃ 建议复测确认；≥ 38℃ 或伴明显不适请及时联系医生。</view><view class="tp-tip">3. 体温偏低（低于 35.5℃）且伴畏寒、乏力等不适，同样建议复测并注意保暖。</view></view></view>